#: ../../install/guidelines.rst:6
msgid "How to Upgrade"
msgstr "如何升级"

#: ../../install/guidelines.rst:8
msgid ""
"If you're doing an upgrade install (rather than a fresh install), "
"there's two suggested approaches: either install Zeek using the same "
"installation prefix directory as before, or pick a new prefix and copy "
"local customizations over."
msgstr ""
"如果你想进行一次升级（而不是全新的安装），推荐两种方式：要么在以前相同的"
"安装目录路径下面安装，要么选择新的目录，然后把本地的修改拷贝过去。"

#: ../../install/guidelines.rst:13
msgid ""
"In the following we summarize general guidelines for upgrading, see the :"
"ref:`release-notes` for version-specific information."
msgstr ""
"下面我们总结普遍的升级指南，见 :ref:`release-notes` 查看版本相关的信息。"

#: ../../install/guidelines.rst:18
msgid "Reusing Previous Install Prefix"
msgstr "使用相同的安装路径"

#: ../../install/guidelines.rst:20
msgid ""
"If you choose to configure and install Zeek with the same prefix "
"directory as before, first stop all running Zeek instances in your "
"cluster (if using ZeekControl, issue the \"zeekctl stop\" command on the "
"manager host).  Next, make a backup of the Zeek install prefix directory."
msgstr ""
"如果你选择在相同路径下配置和安装Zeek，首先停止集群的所有运行中的Zeek实例"
"（如果使用ZeekControl，在管理主机上执行“zeekctl stop”命令）。之后，对Zeek"
"安装目录做一次备份。"

#: ../../install/guidelines.rst:25
msgid ""
"During the upgrade, any file in the install prefix may be overwritten or "
"removed, except for local customization of files in the ``$prefix/share/"
"zeek/site`` and ``$prefix/etc`` directories (``$prefix`` indicating the "
"root of where Zeek was installed).  Also, logs generated at run-time "
"won't be touched by the upgrade."
msgstr ""
"升级过程中，安装路径下的任何文件都会被重写或者移除，除了 ``$prefix/share/"
"zeek/site`` 和 ``$prefix/etc`` （``$prefix`` 表示Zeek安装的根目录）两个目"
"录下面的本地文件修改。同样地，运行时生成的日志文件在升级过程中也不会被修"
"改。"

#: ../../install/guidelines.rst:32
msgid ""
"After upgrading, remember to check the ``$prefix/share/zeek/site`` and ``"
"$prefix/etc`` directories for files with a file extension of ``."
"example``, which indicate that the distribution's version of the file "
"differs from the local one, and therefore, may include local changes.  "
"Review the differences and make adjustments as necessary. Use the new "
"version for differences that aren't a result of a local change."
msgstr ""
"在升级后，记得检查 ``$prefix/share/zeek/site`` 和 ``$prefix/etc`` 目录查"
"看是否有 ``.example`` 后缀的文件，它表示这次安装的版本和原本的不同，因"
"此，可能包含本地的一些改动。审查这些不同，根据需要做一些调整。如果不是本"
"地修改，使用两者较新的那个版本。"

#: ../../install/guidelines.rst:39 ../../install/guidelines.rst:60
msgid ""
"Finally, if using ZeekControl, then issue the \"zeekctl deploy\" "
"command.  This command will check for any policy script errors, install "
"the new version of Zeek to all machines in your cluster, and then it "
"will start Zeek."
msgstr ""
"最后，如果使用ZeekControl，然后执行 “zeekctl deploy” 命令。这个命令会检查"
"所有的策略脚本错误，安装最新版本Zeek到所有集群的机器上，然后重启Zeek。"

#: ../../install/guidelines.rst:44
msgid "Using a New Install Prefix"
msgstr "使用新的安装路径"

#: ../../install/guidelines.rst:46
msgid ""
"To install the newer version in a different prefix directory than "
"before, first stop all running Zeek instances in your cluster (if using "
"ZeekControl, then issue a \"zeekctl stop\" command on the manager "
"host).  Next, install the new version of Zeek in a new directory."
msgstr ""
"要安装新版本到一个不同于以前的新路径上，首先停止集群的所有实例（如果使用"
"ZeekControl，在管理主机上执行 “zeekctl stop” 命令）。接下里，安装新版本"
"Zeek到新路径下面。"

#: ../../install/guidelines.rst:51
msgid ""
"Next, copy local customization and configuration files from the ``"
"$prefix/share/zeek/site`` and ``$prefix/etc`` directories to the new "
"location (``$prefix`` indicating the root of where Zeek was originally "
"installed).  Review the files for differences before copying and make "
"adjustments as necessary (use the new version for differences that "
"aren't a result of a local change).  Of particular note, the copied "
"version of ``$prefix/etc/zeekctl.cfg`` is likely to need changes to any "
"settings that specify a pathname."
msgstr ""
"之后，拷贝 ``$prefix/share/zeek/site`` 和 ``$prefix/etc`` 目录下面的本地"
"修改和配置文件到新位置下（``$prefix`` 表示Zeek之前所在的根目录）。拷贝钱"
"审查文件的差异，然后根据需要做出调整（如果本地没有修改，使用两者中较新的"
"版本）。 尤其需要注意的是，可能需要修改拷贝后的 ``$prefix/etc/zeekctl."
"cfg`` 文件中所有使用了路径名称的地方。"
